{"tid":1537697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可能會殺死亡你嘅武器，無色無味無臭","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:57:43.000Z","uid":258411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"93539993a9259b4da2282046af09845e49694101","tid":1537697,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:18:59.000Z","msg":"琴日，起添馬公園嘅和平集會上，無錯係和平集會期間，警方曾三度投下依種武器<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bw3V0Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bw3V0Z.png&h=fc8bf492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無錯係螢光粉，之前831銅鑼灣都應該有機會出現過。902添馬和平集會上投下嘅螢光粉無色無味無臭，粉末會隨風飄揚，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擔遮作用不大</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，會對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">UV 光</span></strong></span>有反應。最後投放時間大概係4點零左右，由直升機投放，沿維多利亞港飛行。<br />\n1. 依種螢光粉，吸入或同皮膚接觸，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會對人體造成傷害？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>會唔會破壞環境？<br />\n2.直升機沿維多利亞海港投放螢光粉，有機會飄去其他地區，例如尖沙咀，誤中副車，中左其他非參與集會人士，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>會唔會做成錯誤逮捕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n我嚴重懷疑昨日警方用依種手段，想試我地水溫，日後有可能會起示威區域大範圍投放螢光粉？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>快啲推上去！！！殺到埋身啦各位！圍捕加螢光粉，再唔響嘅走都無撚得走！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"35be0202c59b0d97d2f7cee759049601762eb329","tid":1537697,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"949d25fa95e84da63eb877d3e3651494f57b84d0","tid":1537697,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"推阿！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc398201f0ee2882ae34da6891d580529e245d51","tid":1537697,"uid":258411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c